01:23:39.014 --> 01:23:41.108
Well, fine.

01:23:42.726 --> 01:23:44.979
I won't come, then.

01:23:46.438 --> 01:23:49.282
I asked you to lunch
because I liked you.

01:23:50.400 --> 01:23:53.028
